entries.MST_FRONTIERHUNTER_MISSION_1000402_DESCR: Your mission is to clear the deep reaches of this mysterious area of all monsters! But watch out, they're tough!
entries.MST_FRONTIERHUNTER_MISSION_1000403_COMME: You're at the end of the mysterious area that appeared beyond the Vortex Gate. The air shakes as an awesome force descends upon you.
entries.MST_FRONTIERHUNTER_MISSION_1000403_DESCR: Your mission is to clear the final area of this mysterious area of all monsters! Beware as this area is unimaginably dangerous!
